oji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f040a5bcdb2dc4e851661845349e6e4e69475b","tid":38181,"uid":65233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T18:47:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Aritaum 唇膏好用定係tolymoly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同一個brand 都有唔同嘅質地<br />\n我試過有個brand 一支勁好用, 另外一隻就勁難上色<br />\n我自己就鐘意aritaum多啲"},{"pid":"1d7bdc7497e3081a440cd2addc9e3cfbbcf7f4cb","tid":38181,"uid":65233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T18:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f1a5cddc0c65d3393ad0a8db53e772c084d3a1","tid":38181,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T18:56:10.000Z","msg":"有冇折"}]}